{"tid":332582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社工羅湖橋讀《零八憲章》被失蹤公安問：誰是雜種？","createTime":"2017-07-23T05:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T05:53:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c649ed2c1f3f97aac06d6c622b1a1f99bbcea79a","tid":332582,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:53:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20098995&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20098995%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170723&d=T8Rla5ECJQFl2tgwsLfgl0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5d418ec2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20098995%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170723&h=7ccf5a4d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20098995&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170723</a><br />\n<br />\n社工羅湖橋讀《零八憲章》被失蹤<br />\n公安問：誰是雜種？<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n基督徒社工呂智恆於周三（19日）晚上7時左右，在羅湖橋宣讀諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波的著作《我沒有敵人》和《零八憲章》，約15分鐘後即被帶走，失蹤8小時後才返港。他在facebook發表逾2,000字的長文，透露「被失蹤」的來龍去脈，提及公安審問時，瀏覽其facebook專頁「起底」，詢問他7.1在警總掛「雜種過主」的橫額有何含義，更追問「雜種是誰」。"}]}